LAYER 2 to end device
step by step manage switch cisco ios command
1. hostname = WWTP
2. disable telnet enable SSH line vty 5 15, enable password = cisco user=admin
3. encyrption password 
4. create vlan dan name vlan

   dengan keterangan sebagai berikut
	vlan 200 switch
	vlan 201 wifi
	vlan 202 finger
	vlan 203 attandance
	vlan 230 IP PC
	vlan 240 IP DHCP
	vlan 250 IP EXT
5. manage port 
	port 1 master dari coreswitch 
	port 2 untuk ext fanvil dan ke pc , ext sebagai WAN dan to pc sebagai LAN
	port 3 Unifi device vlan wifi sebagai native VLAN dan trunk untuk IP DHCP
    port 4 setting port untuk cctv
	interface vlan 200 dengan ip 182.82.200.151 supaya bisa di remote

#NOTE mini switch with ext fanvil vlan 250(WAN) vlan 230(LAN)
#NOTE beberapa versi IOS untuk setting VLAN, dengan command vlan database 

=====Config dasar dan security======
configure terminal hostname WWTP
enable service password-encryption
enable secret cisco
ip domain name local.net crypto key generate rsa 1024
line vty 5 15 transport input ssh login local
username admin privilege 15 secret cisco 
interface Vlan200 ip address 182.82.200.151 255.255.255.0 no shutdown

======Config VLAN & Name==============
conf ter
vlan 200 name IP_SWITCH	
vlan 201	IP_WiFi 
vlan 202	IP_Finger	
vlan 203	Attandance	
vlan 230	IP_PC	
vlan 240	IP_DHCP 
vlan 250	IP_EXT
valn 260    IP_CCTV

configure terminal
interface GigabitEthernet 0/1
 description from core-sw
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 200,201,202,203,230,240,250

interface GigabitEthernet 0/2
 description jumper PC lara
 switchport mode trunk                   
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 230,250        

interface GigabitEthernet 0/3
 description UNIFI
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport trunk native vlan 201
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 201,240

interface GigabitEthernet 0/4
 description CCTV
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 260
wr save exit

#NOTE cek show vlan dan show interface dan show running 